## ICP Fit Assessment

**Strong fit.** Third-year CS, project team in a project-heavy course, exact platform fragmentation pattern.

---

## Interviewer Reflection

**Most important thing learned:**
Students *want* their informal channel separate from their professor's channel. I had been assuming the opposite — that consolidation was the goal. That assumption is wrong.

**What to do differently next time:**
When someone uses a vivid word like "bridge" to describe their role, stop and ask them to define it. I almost moved past it and only realized later how loaded it was.

